hasAttributes.description: Shows who last updated the record.

hasAttributes.name: createdOnBehalfBy
hasAttributes.description: Shows who created the record on behalf of another user.

hasAttributes.name: modifiedOnBehalfBy
hasAttributes.description: Shows who last updated the record on behalf of another user.

hasAttributes.name: overriddenCreatedOn
hasAttributes.description: Date and time that the record was migrated.

hasAttributes.name: importSequenceNumber
hasAttributes.description: Unique identifier of the data import or data migration that created this record.

hasAttributes.name: ownerId
hasAttributes.description: Owner Id

hasAttributes.name: ownerIdType
hasAttributes.description: The type of owner, either User or Team.

hasAttributes.description: Unique identifier for the business unit that owns the record

hasAttributes.name: owningTeam

hasAttributes.name: timeZoneRuleVersionNumber
hasAttributes.description: For internal use only.

hasAttributes.name: UTCConversionTimeZoneCode

hasAttributes.name: versionNumber
hasAttributes.description: Version Number

hasAttributes.name: deviceId
hasAttributes.description: Unique identifier for entity instances

hasAttributes.name: stateCode
hasAttributes.description: Status of the Device

hasAttributes.name: statusCode
hasAttributes.description: Reason for the status of the Device

hasAttributes.name: name
hasAttributes.description: The name of the custom entity.

hasAttributes.name: carrierAIDC
hasAttributes.description: The full UDI carrier of the Automatic Identification and Data Capture (AIDC) technology representation of the bar code string as printed on the packaging of the device - E.g a bar code or RFID.

hasAttributes.name: deviceNumber
hasAttributes.description: Unique instance identifiers assigned to a device by manufacturers other organizations or owners.

hasAttributes.name: deviceStatus
hasAttributes.description: Status of the Device availability.

hasAttributes.name: expirationDate
hasAttributes.description: The date and time beyond which this device is no longer valid or should not be used (if applicable).

hasAttributes.name: location
hasAttributes.description: The place where the device can be found.

hasAttributes.name: lotNumber
hasAttributes.description: Lot number assigned by the manufacturer.

hasAttributes.name: manufacturer
hasAttributes.description: A name of the manufacturer.

hasAttributes.name: manufacturerDate
hasAttributes.description: The date and time when the device was manufactured.

hasAttributes.name: model
hasAttributes.description: The "model" is an identifier assigned by the manufacturer to identify the product by its type. This number is shared by the all devices sold as the same type.

hasAttributes.name: owner
hasAttributes.description: An organization that is responsible for the provision and ongoing maintenance of the device.

hasAttributes.name: patient
hasAttributes.description: Demographics and other administrative information about an individual or animal receiving care or other health-related services.

hasAttributes.name: type
hasAttributes.description: Code or identifier to identify a kind of device.

hasAttributes.name: UDI
hasAttributes.description: Unique device identifier (UDI) assigned to device label or package.

hasAttributes.name: UDICarrierHRF
hasAttributes.description: Unique device identifier (UDI) assigned to device label or package.

hasAttributes.name: UDIEntryType
hasAttributes.description: A coded entry to indicate how the data was entered.

hasAttributes.name: UDIIssuer
hasAttributes.description: Organization that is charged with issuing UDIs for devices

hasAttributes.name: udiJurisdiction
hasAttributes.description: The identity of the authoritative source for UDI generation within a jurisdiction. All UDIs are globally unique within a single namespace with the appropriate repository uri as the system.

hasAttributes.name: URL
hasAttributes.description: A network address on which the device may be contacted directly.

hasAttributes.name: version
hasAttributes.description: The version of the device, if the device has multiple releases under the same model, or if the device is software or carries firmware.

definitions.description: This entity identifies an instance or a type of a manufactured item that is used in the provision of healthcare without being substantially changed through that activity.
